    <item>
      <title>继石油之后，俄罗斯可能正在打造一支影子天然气舰队</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/after-oil-russia-may-now-be-building-a-shadow-fleet-for-gas</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在入侵乌克兰并遭到西方制裁的几个月后，俄罗斯组建了一支影子舰队，将石油运往世界各地。现在有越来越多的证据表明，莫斯科已经开始对液化天然气采取同样的行动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/after-oil-russia-may-now-be-building-a-shadow-fleet-for-gas</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 10:16:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
